      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an approachable price. It shows its age and wear, but it remains a practical choice for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone needing inexpensive wheels. A straightforward value with plenty of utility for the money.",
