    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car looking for its next owner. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants affordable wheels, a handy runabout, or a project with potential. Easy on the wallet compared with most cars out there, and a great chance to get into something usable without spending big. If you\u2019re after straightforward value and don\u2019t mind a bit of age and character, this one could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with a strong-running powertrain and good bones for someone who wants dependable transportation or a straightforward project. It shows age cosmetically, but the engine pulls well, the transmission shifts as it should, and it tracks down the road with confidence. A practical, no-nonsense car that\u2019s been kept serviceable and still has plenty of usable life left for the next owner. Great value for a commuter, first car, or weekend fixer with real potential.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
